Mauritius Economic Growth Slowing in 2012-2014, Week-End Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-08-07T10:44:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-07/mauritius-economic-growth-slowing-in-2012-2014-week-end-says.html
The Mauritian economic growth rate
will slow to 4 percent from 2012 to 2014 instead of recovering
to 5 percent, Port Louis-based Week-End reported, citing a
circular from Financial Secretary Ali Mansoor.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis via Johannesburg at 
1933 or  gbell16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
